569
00:26:11,990 --> 00:26:12,470
Come on.

570
00:26:12,490 --> 00:26:13,900
Let's recite

571
00:26:13,930 --> 00:26:16,030
the Scripture of Forgetting Emotions.

572
00:26:16,970 --> 00:26:18,340
-Forgetting emotions…
-Shut up!

573
00:26:18,370 --> 00:26:20,490
I can't stand you Eternals and your scriptures!

574
00:26:20,550 --> 00:26:21,270
All you do

575
00:26:21,270 --> 00:26:22,110
is waste time!

576
00:26:22,110 --> 00:26:23,200
-Exactly.
-You…

577
00:26:27,170 --> 00:26:29,920
We're all here for the Wutong Martial Arts Contest,

578
00:26:29,950 --> 00:26:31,920
so why fight over something pointless?

579
00:26:31,940 --> 00:26:32,770
Bah!

580
00:26:32,830 --> 00:26:33,580
The Eternals from Kunlun

581
00:26:33,600 --> 00:26:34,750
