608
00:27:26,120 --> 00:27:27,440
But you're weak and incompetent,

609
00:27:27,460 --> 00:27:29,330
causing chaos in the whole city.

610
00:27:29,350 --> 00:27:30,550
If I were you,

611
00:27:30,580 --> 00:27:32,850
I'd have already buried myself in a hole.

612
00:27:32,880 --> 00:27:34,150
You don't deserve to come here

613
00:27:34,170 --> 00:27:35,900
and fight with us for the Wutong Spirit Pill.

614
00:27:35,930 --> 00:27:36,520
Nan Wan!

615
00:27:36,540 --> 00:27:37,620
That's nonsense!

616
00:27:37,640 --> 00:27:38,960
If Chong Zhao doesn't deserve to be here,

617
00:27:38,980 --> 00:27:40,430
