641
00:28:46,990 --> 00:28:48,160
He's so powerful.

642
00:28:48,200 --> 00:28:48,960
Forget it.

643
00:28:48,960 --> 00:28:50,230
The second-tier rooms will do too.

644
00:28:50,860 --> 00:28:51,830
Forget it.

645
00:29:06,340 --> 00:29:07,180
