651
00:29:19,810 --> 00:29:23,070
Kill them! Kill them!

652
00:29:23,570 --> 00:29:24,440
Go!

653
00:29:24,470 --> 00:29:28,040
Kill them! Kill them!

654
00:29:30,090 --> 00:29:33,390
Kill them! Kill them!

