00:30:00,310 --> 00:30:01,510
[Hu, a Yi citizen]

674
00:30:02,170 --> 00:30:03,100
Chong Zhao.

675
00:30:03,130 --> 00:30:04,410
What's wrong with this kid?

676
00:30:04,720 --> 00:30:06,540
