680
00:30:12,420 --> 00:30:13,830
If we kill them,

681
00:30:13,850 --> 00:30:14,920
the kid can be saved!

682
00:30:14,950 --> 00:30:16,800
Right, kill them! Kill them!

683
00:30:16,820 --> 00:30:18,240
