00:31:02,790 --> 00:31:03,590
Hu!

710
00:31:05,100 --> 00:31:06,230
Listen.

711
00:31:06,260 --> 00:31:07,700
Take her away.

712
00:31:07,720 --> 00:31:08,840
If she dies here,

713
00:31:08,870 --> 00:31:09,930
