765
00:33:35,160 --> 00:33:36,050
Thanks

766
00:33:36,650 --> 00:33:37,570
for the pill.

767
00:33:38,140 --> 00:33:38,970
Earlier,

768
00:33:39,230 --> 00:33:40,400
